		<div id="comment_body_65286091"><p>About the same as saying "Why are you depressed? Just think positively!"<br>Addiction to social media is called an addiction because it affects the brain's chemistry and, to make matters worse, it has a social component where if you don't participate, you will ostracize yourself from your social peers who do.<br>Us adults can resist the siren call relatively well because we remember a world without it. For today's children, it IS their world.</p></div>
